rComments: By far the worst instructor I have encountered in my academic career. She refuses to outline expectations for assignments and grading criteria is arbitrary at best. Demonstrates a complete lack of empathy and kindness for her students when they are struggling. I went to her office hours for help and was told to drop out.
Assignments expectations are unclear, instructor is unsympathetic and lacking in pedagogical skill.
I love that in a graduate course she wanted people to let her know if they were going to the bathroom. Clearly, she's a bit deranged!
appeared completely uninterested in subject matter; criticisms on evaluated work were baseless; by far the worst class I have ever attended; no pedagogical skills or human kindness apparent
